[SHORT DESC]
Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/iron_tail">Iron Tail</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/iron_tail">Iron Tail</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>The foe is slammed with a sturdy tail of steel. It may also lower the target's Defense stat if it hits.</p>